{
  "stem": "26142.11",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he got to Chust with his brother.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got to Chust, and we stayed there overnight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people wanted to give us a bed, but we didn't even want to get into a bed.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew we were very filthy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But my father had a business associate by the name of David Schwartz-- that was a wealthy family that lived in-- this family that he dropped us off was a poor family.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The house, I don't I don't even think that they had inside, inside plumbing in that house.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was at the edge of the city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We wanted to get to this family, David Schwartz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Next, next day during, during, during the day we were able to, to get over there to this family, Da-- David Schwartz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They, they took us in, very, very, very-- we were very happy and surprised.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We still didn't know why this Dudie Neuman, what what he said.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We found that out later.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in-- and in this house, the first thing what we did was ask for a bath, but-- because in four months time-- I don't remember exactly the date where it was, but it was a good four months that we didn't have a bath.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we stayed in that house.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the next day-- I, I think either the next or the th-- second day [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] after, after we, we, we bathed, and we were-- I, I fell asleep from exhaustion.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was-- I slept 12 hours, and then I slept-- all of sudden I remember I, I wake up, and I hear the voice of my father.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "My father came from Mlawa to Chust, and he knew where we are going to be.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
